g hull

# Nose tip to nose ring
f 1 5 2
f 1 2 4
f 1 4 3
f 1 3 5

# Nose ring to front ring (build 8 triangles around)
f 2 6 5
f 5 6 9
f 5 9 3
f 3 9 7
f 3 7 4
f 4 7 8
f 4 8 2
f 2 8 6

